The paper discusses the use of Self Organizing Maps (SOM) and Growing Hierarchical SOM (GHSOM) for data analysis, which falls under the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised learning, which is a common technique in Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of GHSOM for image analysis, which falls under the category of Computer Vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses the development of an interface tool, which falls under the category of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
